voctomix (0.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release with mostly bugfixes, but also a few new features.
  * debian/rules:
    - remove privacy breaches in README.md as they are not useful in
      voctomix.html in the package. (They are useful in the rendered README.md
      on Github though.)
    - Make new-upstream-version target deal with new .dotfiles in source.
  * Bump standards version to 4.1.1, no changes needed.
  * Bump debian/compat to 10 and build-depend on debhelper >= 10.2.5~.

 -- Holger Levsen <holger@debian.org>  Fri, 29 Sep 2017 15:52:18 +0200

